 <span data-ttu-id="69900-105">藉由使用<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PowerEase>函式，您可以指定如何快速地加速或減速會藉由指定<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PowerEase.Power%2A>屬性：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69900-105">By using the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PowerEase> function, you can specify how quickly acceleration/deceleration takes place by specifying the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PowerEase.Power%2A> property:</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="69900-106">*f*(*t*) = *t*<sup>p</sup>其中`p`等於<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PowerEase.Power%2A>屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69900-106">*f*(*t*) = *t*<sup>p</sup> where `p` is equal to the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PowerEase.Power%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
